{"tid":2083725,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉巧琦：港區國安法生效前的行為或被用作持續犯罪舉證","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T03:40:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08ac975c37a7457e18b90f471192798453af4758","tid":2083725,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534626-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534626-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=b2c672fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534626-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5251fb3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534626-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有報道指，「港區國安法」中有罪行的最高刑罰是終身監禁。大律師公會副主席葉巧琦表示，在本港判囚終身的罪行包括強姦、販毒及謀殺等，有關罪行刑罰屬社會共識，不過目前「港區國安法」的4個罪行，連定義都不知道，之前公布的草案說明亦都無提及刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n葉巧琦在一個電台節目說，根據普通法，要證明一個罪名就要有持續犯罪的證據。而「港區國安法」生效前作出的行為，是有機會被用作持續犯罪的舉證。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，《基本法》有訂明可維持陪審團制度，對於有意見指審理「港區國安法」時可以不設陪審團，令人擔憂。"},{"pid":"159340a0d19ae46a0194c8f148b30343e0b8aef9","tid":2083725,"uid":63885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0FfDNm.jpg&amp;h=a1fd880b&amp;s=540 \" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCDMLss.jpg&amp;h=2a905b11&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"88c27c77024fe0336fa2274f1a27abb5d61ba2fd","tid":2083725,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d66f7ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KDBrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\